- Based on application, the market is categorized into oncology, infectious diseases, cardiovascular diseases, autoimmune disorders, others.
- By end user, the market is divided into hospitals, home care settings, clinics, others.
- Geographically, the market is analyzed across North America, Europe, Asia-Pacific, South America, Middle East and Africa.

